47
00:04:09,060 --> 00:04:11,560
历史的轨迹不断地重复着
A pattern repeating itself endlessly.

48
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:16,900
帕尔瓦娜 我年轻的时候
When I was young, Parvana,

49
