for a while at least.

53
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,680
但好景不长
But it did not last.

54
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,550
我们的国土变得脆弱不堪
The ground became weak under our feet,

55
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:37,890
