then a civil war.

58
00:04:43,990 --> 00:04:45,560
如此的混乱局面下
In the chaos,

59
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:48,700
有些人希望领袖可以恢复秩序
some looked to those who might restore order.

60
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,730
