Am I getting married?

111
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:28,860
当然不是 你还是个孩子呢
Of course not. You are still a child.

112
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:31,260
我现在只想让你天天玩耍 讲讲故事就好
I want you playing and telling stories.

113
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:33,130
我长大了 不愿意讲什么故事了
I'm too old for that now.

114
00:07:33,130 --> 00:07:36,230
长大了就不爱故事了？ 你一直很爱故事啊
Too old for stories? You've always loved stories.

115
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:38,170
讲故事能有什么用？
What's the use?

116
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:52,980
我跟你妈妈谈几句 一切都会好起来的
I'll have a word with Mama-jan and we'll sort it all out.

117
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,720
求你别提那裙子的事
Please don't mention the dress.

118
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:02,890
要不她会唠叨个没完的
Then I'll never hear the end of it.

119
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:05,230
- 什么没完？ - 没事 妈妈
- The end of what? - Nothing, Mama-jan.

120
00:08:05,230 --> 00:08:07,860
我们不卖帕尔瓦娜的漂亮裙子了
We're not selling Parvana's good dress.

121
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:10,360
爸爸 我说的不是这个
Baba, that's not what I meant.

122
00:08:10,370 --> 00:08:12,430
我们需要钱 孩子她爸
We need the money, Baba.

123
