Do you know what it means?

658
00:51:16,820 --> 00:51:18,490
不知道
No.

659
00:51:19,720 --> 00:51:23,620
有时候 在你透过晴朗的夜空看月亮时
Sometimes, on a clear night when you look at the moon,

660
00:51:23,620 --> 00:51:26,290
能看到月亮被一条明亮的光圈围绕着
you can see a bright outline around it.

661
00:51:27,530 --> 00:51:30,930
那条光圈就叫作哈拉
That outline is called hala.

662
00:51:30,930 --> 00:51:34,370
我妻子以它来取名
My wife was named for that light.

663
00:51:43,540 --> 00:51:45,340
- 给你 - 这太多了
- Here. - This is too much.

664
00:51:45,350 --> 00:51:47,580
别推辞
Don't argue with me.

665
00:51:47,580 --> 00:51:48,820
谢谢你
Thank you.

666
00:52:00,390 --> 00:52:04,060
好啦 扎西 我可以揪你的吗？
Stop it, Zaki. Can I pull yours?

667
00:52:06,100 --> 00:52:08,930
让他安静点 我还想睡觉呢
Keep him quiet. I'm trying to sleep.

668
00:52:08,940 --> 00:52:12,840
- 你犯什么毛病呢？ - 要不你给扎西讲个故事吧 好不好？
- What's the matter with you? - Why don't you tell Zaki a story, hmm?

669
00:52:12,840 --> 00:52:14,540
我们都很喜欢
We'd all like that.

670
00:52:14,540 --> 00:52:17,910
好吧 扎西 你想听故事里的小男孩后来怎么样了吗？
Well, Zaki, do you want to know what happened to the boy?

671
00:52:19,610 --> 00:52:21,880
好的 好的 还有大象
Yes, yes, and the elephant.

672
00:52:23,450 --> 00:52:27,750
男孩跑啊跑 他很害怕 心跳得特别快
The boy ran and ran, his heart beating fast in fear.

673
00:52:27,760 --> 00:52:30,920
身后追逐他的东西丝毫没有停下的意思
And the thing that chased him never stopped.

674
00:52:33,690 --> 00:52:37,500
于是小男孩非常害怕地躲在树后
So the boy hid behind a tree and he waited for courage.

675
00:52:44,870 --> 00:52:48,110
一位老妇人想要挤山羊奶
An ancient woman had been trying to milk a goat,

676
00:52:48,110 --> 00:52:50,540
可她后背酸痛难忍
but her back was very sore.

677
00:52:50,540 --> 00:52:55,980
我的背好痛啊
My back is very sore.

678
00:52:55,980 --> 00:53:00,620
男孩很同情老妇人 于是让老妇人在树荫下休息
The boy took pity on her and told her to rest under the shade of a tree

679
00:53:00,620 --> 00:53:02,690
他来挤羊奶
and he would do the milking instead.

680
00:53:02,690 --> 00:53:04,790
您到树荫下坐着吧
Please sit under the shade of this tree,

681
00:53:04,790 --> 00:53:07,460
我来帮您挤
and I will do the milking instead.

682
00:53:14,700 --> 00:53:16,740
当他挤完羊奶后
When he finished milking the goat,

683
00:53:16,740 --> 00:53:19,840
老妇人与他分享美味又温暖的羊奶
the old woman shared the lovely, warm milk with him.

684
00:53:19,840 --> 00:53:23,810
这是他喝过最好喝的羊奶
It was the nicest milk he had ever tasted,

685
00:53:23,810 --> 00:53:26,480
于是他称赞老了妇人的羊群
and he complimented the woman on her goats.

686
00:53:26,480 --> 00:53:28,680
您山羊的产奶量真多
Your goats are very generous.

687
00:53:28,680 --> 00:53:31,920
老妇人给男孩一面镜子作为回报
In return, the old woman gave him a mirror.

688
00:53:31,920 --> 00:53:36,120
看 多闪啊
See how it shines!

689
00:53:36,120 --> 00:53:38,620
得到镜子后 男孩非常高兴
The boy was delighted with the mirror,

690
00:53:38,630 --> 00:53:43,730
但他看着镜子时 镜子照出了尾随他的东西
but as he looked into it, he saw the reflection of the thing that followed him!

691
00:53:48,030 --> 00:53:49,700
妈妈 你在做什么？
What are you doing, Mama-jan?

692
00:53:49,700 --> 00:53:52,500
我在收拾苏拉娅的衣服
I'm laying out Soraya's good clothes.

693
00:53:52,510 --> 00:53:54,840
这些衣服要我拿到市场去卖吗？
Am I to sell them at the market?

694
00:53:54,840 --> 00:53:57,850
嘘 帕尔瓦娜 该睡觉了
Shh, shh, shh, Parvana. It's time to sleep.

695
00:54:05,990 --> 00:54:09,620
我得想方设法去白沙瓦
I just need to find a way to get to Peshawar,

696
00:54:09,620 --> 00:54:11,760
在那里我会计划出属于我的未来
and I can figure it out from there.

697
00:54:11,760 --> 00:54:14,160
我想果阿会有海滩
I think there's a beach in Goa

698
00:54:14,160 --> 00:54:16,530
那的游客非常富有
where the tourists are very rich.

699
00:54:16,530 --> 00:54:18,730
如果他们有钱 那我的蓝色石头就能卖出去了
If they're rich, they would buy my blue stones,

700
00:54:18,730 --> 00:54:22,070
在那我就能经营我的小生意了 届时你就可以跟我合伙干了
and that's where I'd set up my business, and you could join me.

701
00:54:22,070 --> 00:54:24,200
在我找到爸爸后
Once I find Baba.

702
00:54:24,200 --> 00:54:26,540
嗯 在你找到你爸爸后
Once you find your Baba.

703
00:54:45,790 --> 00:54:47,090
100
100.

704
00:54:47,090 --> 00:54:48,590
85呗
I'll give you 85.

705
00:54:48,600 --> 00:54:49,830
- 90最低 - 82怎么样
- Ninety. - Eighty-two.

706
00:54:49,830 --> 00:54:51,830
最少85了
Eighty-five, and that's final.

707
00:54:51,830 --> 00:54:54,470
再加上一串葡萄 就这么定了
Eighty-five and a bunch of grapes, and that's final.

708
00:54:59,240 --> 00:55:03,710
你写字下笔太重了 但字写得不错
You're leaning too hard on the pen, but your writing is good.

709
00:55:03,710 --> 00:55:06,480
如果你再温柔一点 写好字会更容易些
If you try it more gently, it'll be easier.

710
00:55:43,280 --> 00:55:45,650
等等 请等一下
Wait! Wait a moment!

711
00:55:47,290 --> 00:55:49,150
什么事？
What is it, child?

712
00:55:49,160 --> 00:55:52,860
你曾问过我之前坐在我身边的那...那个老师的情况
You asked me before about the man who used to sit there... the teacher.

713
00:55:52,860 --> 00:55:55,990
- 你叔叔？ - 他不是去了马扎里沙里夫
- Your uncle? - He didn't go to Mazar-e-Sharif.

714
00:55:56,000 --> 00:55:59,160
我叔叔进了监狱 然而他是冤枉的
He was taken to prison. But he did nothing wrong.

715
00:55:59,170 --> 00:56:00,730
- 哪一个？ - 什么哪一个？
- Which one? - What?

716
00:56:00,730 --> 00:56:03,030
- 哪所监狱？ - 普利查西监狱
- Which prison? - Pul-e-Charkhi.

717
00:56:03,040 --> 00:56:06,570
已经过了几个星期了 但仍就杳无音信
It's been weeks now, and my family has had no word of him.

718
00:56:08,640 --> 00:56:10,610
星期三去监狱一趟吧
Go to the prison on Wednesday.

719
00:56:10,610 --> 00:56:12,280
去找我表弟罗尚帮忙
Ask for Roshan. He's my cousin.

720
00:56:12,280 --> 00:56:15,850
告诉他是拉扎克让你来的 他力所能及的话 就会帮你的
Tell him Razaq sent you and he will help you, if he can.

721
00:56:42,280 --> 00:56:43,680
德利瓦
Deliwar!

722
00:56:43,680 --> 00:56:49,180
照这样干下去 等我到海边的那天 我都变成风烛残年的老太太了
With work like this, I'll be an old woman by the time I get to the sea.

723
00:56:49,180 --> 00:56:52,020
或是个老头儿
Or an old man.

724
00:56:57,220 --> 00:57:01,330
你坐着休息下 我给你讲个故事
You sit and rest, Deliwar, and I'll tell you a story.

725
00:57:01,330 --> 00:57:04,600
- 故事？ - 对呀
- A story? - Yes, a story.

726
00:57:05,700 --> 00:57:07,260
在很久很久以前
One time in the deep past,

727
00:57:07,270 --> 00:57:11,840
从前有一个小男孩 他要把怪物偷走的袋子带回到村里 袋子里装着的是十分珍贵的种子
there was a boy who had to return a stolen bag of precious seeds to his village.

728
00:57:11,840 --> 00:57:15,270
是个喜剧吗 还是...悲剧呢？
Is it a happy story or a sad story?

729
00:57:15,280 --> 00:57:17,580
你听完就知道了
Just wait and see.

730
00:57:18,910 --> 00:57:21,950
男孩得知 必须集齐三件事物
The boy had been told he needed three things

731
00:57:21,950 --> 00:57:25,120
才能战胜象王
in order to overcome the Elephant King...

732
00:57:25,120 --> 00:57:28,990
一件闪着光 一件用来抓捕的 和...
something that shines, something that ensnares and something that...

733
00:57:28,990 --> 00:57:31,860
喂 你们两个 过来
Hey, you two! Come here!

734
00:57:33,230 --> 00:57:35,060
来啊
Come on!

735
00:57:35,060 --> 00:57:36,660
我认识他
I know that boy.

736
00:57:36,660 --> 00:57:39,200
快点 马上过来
Hurry up. Come here.

737
00:57:39,200 --> 00:57:40,830
快点啊
Come on.

738
00:57:40,830 --> 00:57:43,640
我们最好听他的话过去
We'd better do what we're told.

739
00:57:46,740 --> 00:57:48,780
赶快啊 懒鬼
Get a move on, lazy kids.

740
00:57:56,980 --> 00:57:59,020
这就是新来的苦力？
So these are the new workers?

741
00:57:59,020 --> 00:58:01,890
快回答啊 你们是傻子吗？
Where are your tongues? Are you stupid?

742
00:58:01,890 --> 00:58:05,090
伊德瑞斯提议用掰手腕的方式来做个小测验
Idrees suggested we have a little arm-wrestling match.

743
00:58:06,090 --> 00:58:09,190
看看你们是否有资格为我工作
To see if you're strong enough to work for me.

744
00:58:09,200 --> 00:58:11,830
我看到你坐在那儿偷懒
I saw you sitting down over there instead of working.

745
00:58:11,830 --> 00:58:13,830
停下 伊德瑞斯
Idrees, stop now.

746
00:58:13,830 --> 00:58:15,800
给我来杯茶水
Make me some tea.

747
00:58:19,770 --> 00:58:22,710
小不点 让我见识下你有多废物
Let me see how feeble you are, little one.

748
00:58:23,980 --> 00:58:26,250
这弱鸡连手都抬不起来
He can't even lift his hand.

749
00:58:27,880 --> 00:58:30,180
起来吧 端点茶水来
Get up and make us tea.

750
00:58:31,450 --> 00:58:34,920
叔叔 我觉得你需要招新工人了
Uncle, I think you need new workers.

751
00:58:34,920 --> 00:58:37,790
- 这两个简直太废了 - 够了 伊德瑞斯
- These ones are no good. - Enough, Idrees.

752
00:58:37,790 --> 00:58:39,420
别难为这些可怜的娃了
Leave the poor kids alone.

753
00:58:39,430 --> 00:58:41,930
他们俩还是太嫩
They are a little undercooked.

754
00:58:45,770 --> 00:58:48,070
我知道你
I know you.

755
00:58:48,070 --> 00:58:50,270
你是那个老师的女...
You're the teacher's daugh...

756
00:58:55,740 --> 00:58:57,880
伊德瑞斯
Idrees.

757
00:58:57,880 --> 00:58:59,880
把枪拿回来
Bring the gun back!

758
00:58:59,880 --> 00:59:01,910
我说了 把枪拿回来
I said bring the gun back!

759
00:59:01,910 --> 00:59:04,820
伊德瑞斯
Idrees!

760
00:59:23,240 --> 00:59:25,040
滚出来
Come out now!

761
00:59:28,380 --> 00:59:30,410
给我滚出来
Come out now!

762
00:59:30,410 --> 00:59:33,710
伊德瑞斯 战争已经开始了 我们要向西转移
Idrees, it has begun! We are moving west.

763
00:59:34,780 --> 00:59:37,550
我们接到命令要立刻行动
We have been given orders to go immediately!

764
00:59:37,550 --> 00:59:39,780
我知道你是谁
I know who you are!

765
00:59:39,790 --> 00:59:41,290
你听见了吗？
Do you hear?

766
00:59:42,390 --> 00:59:44,490
快上来 快
Get up here! Come on!

767
00:59:46,230 --> 00:59:48,860
现在就上来 你个怂包
Right now! You little coward!

768
00:59:50,900 --> 00:59:54,870
你不是想参战吗？ 现在你的机会来了
You want to fight? Now is your chance to fight!

769
00:59:56,840 --> 00:59:58,240
做个男人吧
You become a man.

770
01:00:21,200 --> 01:00:23,490
他走了
He's gone.

771
01:00:23,500 --> 01:00:25,560
他要是回来了呢？
What if he comes back?

772
01:00:25,570 --> 01:00:27,870
那只能算他运气好
He'd be lucky.

773
01:00:27,870 --> 01:00:29,430
我们这是在哪？
Where are we?

774
01:00:29,440 --> 01:00:31,840
我逃跑时候来过这里一次
I came here once when I ran away.

775
01:00:31,840 --> 01:00:35,910
不知道是我身体长大了 还是进来的洞口变窄了
I think the way in has gotten smaller or I have gotten bigger.

776
01:00:36,610 --> 01:00:38,380
这东西看起来有点历史了
It looks old.

777
01:00:39,280 --> 01:00:40,950
我丢了一只鞋
I lost a shoe.

778
01:00:40,950 --> 01:00:44,450
我帽子也丢了 可我觉得它就在外面
I lost my cap, although I think it's outside.

779
01:00:44,450 --> 01:00:46,290
你为什么揍他？
Why did you hit him?

780
01:00:48,860 --> 01:00:51,360
把我爸绑走的那伙人里有他一个
When they took my father, he was one of them.

781
01:00:53,490 --> 01:00:55,230
再给我讲讲那个男孩吧
Tell me more about the boy.

782
01:00:55,230 --> 01:00:56,930
什么男孩？
What boy?

783
01:00:56,930 --> 01:00:58,900
故事里的那个男孩
The story boy.

784
01:00:58,900 --> 01:01:01,630
男孩觉得很冷
The boy was cold.

785
01:01:01,630 --> 01:01:05,240
虽然太阳挂在空中 他却感受不到一丝温暖
Though the sun burned in the sky, it gave no heat.

786
01:01:05,240 --> 01:01:08,240
但是他有一个又大又暖的外套
But he had a warm hat and a big coat.

787
01:01:08,240 --> 01:01:09,970
不 他没有
No, he didn't.

788
01:01:09,980 --> 01:01:12,440
他已经发现三件事物中的一件了...
He had already found one of the three things...

789
01:01:12,450 --> 01:01:14,350
一个闪光的镜子
a mirror that shone.

790
01:01:14,350 --> 01:01:17,980
但是当他往镜子里看时 他看到了他身后的东西
But when he looked at it, he saw something behind him.

791
01:01:17,990 --> 01:01:20,650
那东西很吓人 非常恐怖
Something scary. Something dreadful!

792
01:01:20,650 --> 01:01:23,620
- 是一匹马 - 不 什沃吉亚 不是一匹马
- A horse! - No, Shauzia, not a horse.

793
01:01:23,620 --> 01:01:25,520
是啊 就是一匹马
Yes, it was.

794
01:01:25,530 --> 01:01:29,130
还是一匹非常老的马 走起路来骨头都咔哒咔哒响
And it was a very old horse whose bones clattered together when it walked.

795
01:01:29,130 --> 01:01:32,360
这一点都不吓人
It wasn't scary at all.

796
01:01:32,370 --> 01:01:36,670
好吧  看到老马的样子 男孩感到很难过 于是他喂了它一些干草
Fine. The boy felt sad for the old horse and fed him hay.

797
01:01:36,670 --> 01:01:38,640
然后他们都过上了幸福的生活
And they all lived happily ever after.

798
01:01:38,640 --> 01:01:41,370
我才讲到故事的一半 这不是结局
It's the middle of the story, not the end!

799
01:01:41,380 --> 01:01:44,140
从一个石室的门里
From a door carved into the stone,

800
01:01:44,140 --> 01:01:46,440
走出来一个胖子
out came a round man.

801
01:01:46,450 --> 01:01:50,510
你竟然把我的干草浪费在一匹即将死去的老马身上
You wasted my hay on an old horse that will soon be dead!

802
01:01:50,520 --> 01:01:53,620
胖子把男孩扔进了一口古井的深处
The round man threw the boy deep into the belly of an ancient well.

803
01:01:53,620 --> 01:01:56,220
啊..
Aaah!

804
01:01:57,490 --> 01:02:00,120
在井的底部有绿宝石
At the bottom of the well there were emeralds,

805
01:02:00,130 --> 01:02:04,200
胖子想让男孩把绿宝石拿给他 作为男孩浪费干草的补偿
and the round man wanted them brought up to him as payment for the wasted hay.

806
01:02:04,200 --> 01:02:06,560
你得把那些绿宝石拿给我
You will bring the emeralds to me.

807
01:02:06,570 --> 01:02:08,600
- 他的名字是？ - 你问的是那个胖子的？
- What's his name? - The round man?

808
01:02:08,600 --> 01:02:10,370
不是 是那个男孩的名字
No, the boy.

809
01:02:10,370 --> 01:02:13,600
你不能光讲人家男孩的故事 不给人家起个名字
You can't have a story about a boy and not give him a name.

810
01:02:13,610 --> 01:02:15,540
你不起我可要给他起名字了啊
Give him a name before I do.

811
01:02:15,540 --> 01:02:17,410
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

812
01:02:17,410 --> 01:02:19,910
他叫苏莱曼
His name is Sulayman.

813
01:02:20,550 --> 01:02:22,380
这是个好名字
That's a good name.

814
01:02:22,380 --> 01:02:25,350
苏莱曼倒在井的底部
Sulayman lay at the bottom of the well.

815
01:02:25,350 --> 01:02:28,450
突然 他看到了几具骷髅
Suddenly, he could see skeletons.

816
01:02:28,450 --> 01:02:33,290
一共3具骷髅 它们的骨手里都攥着一颗绿宝石
Three skeletons, each with an emerald clutched in its bony hands.

817
01:02:33,290 --> 01:02:35,130
- 他大声呼救 - 救命
- He called out for help. - Help!

818
01:02:35,130 --> 01:02:38,260
那匹可怜的老马从井口向下望着他
The poor old horse looked back at him from way above.

819
01:02:38,260 --> 01:02:41,170
然后它做了一件很神奇的事情
But the horse did something extraordinary.

820
01:02:41,170 --> 01:02:44,100
它发出了世界上所有种动物的叫声
He neighed with the voice of all the world's animals.

821
01:02:53,750 --> 01:02:57,050
苏莱曼爬啊爬 终于爬到了井的顶部
Sulayman climbed up, up, all the way to the top,

822
01:02:57,050 --> 01:02:59,420
然后他对救他一命的老马表示了感谢
and he thanked the horse for saving his life.

823
01:02:59,420 --> 01:03:02,260
谢谢你救了我的命
Thank you for saving my life.

824
01:03:07,130 --> 01:03:09,590
苏莱曼拿到了那三块宝石
Sulayman had just three emeralds with him...

825
01:03:09,600 --> 01:03:12,600
于是他要求胖子用食物来换
And asked the round man for food in return.

826
01:03:12,600 --> 01:03:14,330
他很饿
He was hungry.

827
01:03:14,330 --> 01:03:16,600
但那胖子即卑鄙又很小气
But the round man was wicked and cheap.

828
01:03:16,600 --> 01:03:20,470
他扔给了苏莱曼一个渔网 让他自己捕鱼吃
He threw a fishing net at Sulayman and he told him to get his own food.

829
01:03:20,470 --> 01:03:23,740
- 这网正是苏莱曼所需之物 - 哈哈
- That was exactly what Sulayman needed. - Ha-ha!

830
01:03:23,740 --> 01:03:26,140
那件用来抓捕的事物
Something that ensnares.

831
01:03:26,150 --> 01:03:27,750
但在苏莱曼的离开后
But as Sulayman left,

832
01:03:27,750 --> 01:03:31,480
三具骷髅的鬼魂从宝石里出来了
the ghosts of the three skeletons came out of the three emeralds

833
01:03:31,490 --> 01:03:34,450
它们在胖子头上缠转盘旋 吓得胖子魂不附体
and swirled and twirled and scared the round man

834
01:03:34,450 --> 01:03:37,760
用如此手段来向害他们丧命的胖子复仇
in frightful vengeance for having lost them their lives.

835
01:03:42,030 --> 01:03:45,660
苏莱曼和那匹老马继续向山那边进发
Sulayman and the horse continued their journey toward the mountain,

836
01:03:45,660 --> 01:03:49,170
但老马越走越慢了
but the horse was getting slower and slower.

837
01:03:49,170 --> 01:03:52,540
它实在是太老了 需要休息
He needed to rest, being very, very old,

838
01:03:52,540 --> 01:03:55,440
于是苏莱曼为它搭了一个帐篷
and so Sulayman made a shelter for the horse

839
01:03:55,440 --> 01:03:58,140
然后让这匹马等他回来
and told him to wait for him.

840
01:03:58,150 --> 01:04:00,510
那匹马有意阻止男孩...
The horse protested...

841
01:04:00,510 --> 01:04:04,450
但苏莱曼知道 象王和它的爪牙
but Sulayman knew he had to face the Elephant King and the jaguars

842
01:04:04,450 --> 01:04:06,080
他必须亲自去面对
all by himself.

843
01:04:06,090 --> 01:04:08,120
我们会再见面的 老伙计
I will see you again, old horse.

844
01:04:10,320 --> 01:04:12,390
说完他就一个人上路了
And so on he went alone.

845
01:04:24,800 --> 01:04:27,140
明天是星期三
Tomorrow is Wednesday.

846
01:04:27,140 --> 01:04:30,140
我要到监狱去了
I'm going back there, to the prison.

847
01:04:31,740 --> 01:04:34,080
他们到时候会让我见我爸爸的
They'll have to let me see him then.

848
01:04:55,270 --> 01:04:57,300
从现在开始 你就别出门了
From now on, you're staying inside.

849
01:04:57,300 --> 01:04:59,570
- 那么做太危险了 - 不 妈妈
- It's much too dangerous. - No, Mama-jan.

850
01:04:59,570 --> 01:05:01,770
- 我们会一起设法逃出来的 - “我们”？
- We manage all right out there. - "We"?

851
01:05:01,780 --> 01:05:05,710
我和德利瓦 她也是个女孩 我们一起工作
Me and Deliwar. She's a girl too. We work together.

852
01:05:05,710 --> 01:05:09,450
我们已经给我表兄写信了 让他们给你姐姐在马扎安排一门亲事
We've written to my cousin to arrange a marriage for your sister in Mazar

853
01:05:09,450 --> 01:05:11,580
他们回信表示同意
They wrote back, and it was accepted.

854
01:05:11,590 --> 01:05:14,450
后天会有人来把我们带走
Someone will come for us the day after tomorrow to take us away.

855
01:05:14,450 --> 01:05:16,350
- 你以后不用再冒险去监狱了 - 什么？
- You don't need to do this anymore. - What?

856
01:05:16,360 --> 01:05:18,360
这日子不能这么过
We can't go on like this.

857
01:05:18,360 --> 01:05:20,860
- 我们不能靠你养活啊 - 为什么？
- We can't depend on you to keep us alive. - Why?

858
01:05:20,860 --> 01:05:22,730
我现在挣的钱足够养家了
I provide for you just fine.

859
01:05:22,730 --> 01:05:24,900
这不是一个孩子的工作
It's not the job of a child.

860
01:05:24,900 --> 01:05:27,430
我们怎么能撇下爸爸离开
How can we leave without Baba?

861
01:05:27,430 --> 01:05:29,900
每天你回家的时候 身上都带着伤口
Every day you come home with cuts and blisters.

862
01:05:29,900 --> 01:05:33,610
每天你出去工作 我都不知能否看到你安然归来
Every day you go out there, and I don't know if I'll see you back again.

863
01:05:34,740 --> 01:05:36,740
我不能连你也失去
I can't lose you too.

864
01:05:36,740 --> 01:05:38,740
我不会去的
I'm not going.

865
01:05:38,740 --> 01:05:41,810
爸爸会回来的 我们走了 家里就没人等他了
Baba could come back, and no one will be here waiting for him.

866
01:05:41,820 --> 01:05:44,250
那我们要等多久
So how long should we wait?

867
01:05:44,250 --> 01:05:46,680
等到他们发现你是女孩 然后也把你从我身边夺走吗？
Until you're found out and taken away from me?

868
01:05:46,690 --> 01:05:48,920
等到我不得不把扎西送出去 来赚钱养家吗？
Until I have to send Zaki out to earn our keep?

869
01:05:48,920 --> 01:05:51,220
在我们离开之前 让我去看看他吧
Let me go see him before we leave.

870
01:05:51,220 --> 01:05:53,420
好让他知道我们要去的是哪
Let me tell him where we are going.

871
01:05:53,430 --> 01:05:55,830
- 帕尔瓦娜 - 让我帮他把手杖带上
- Parvana! - Let me bring him his walking stick.

872
01:05:55,830 --> 01:05:57,560
然后我就跟你走
Then I will go with you.

873
01:05:57,560 --> 01:06:01,500
我会做一个好妹妹 一个好女儿
Then I will be a good sister and a good daughter.

874
01:06:01,500 --> 01:06:03,100
我发誓
I promise.

875
01:06:03,900 --> 01:06:05,510
我保证
I promise.

876
01:06:20,590 --> 01:06:22,250
听话 不要走
Please don't go.

877
01:06:22,260 --> 01:06:24,820
听妈妈的吧  现在外面太危险了
Please, it is much too dangerous now.

878
01:06:24,820 --> 01:06:27,390
妈妈 我走了
Mama-jan, I'm going.

879
01:06:27,390 --> 01:06:29,260
宵禁之前我一定回来
I'll be back tonight before curfew.

880
01:06:29,260 --> 01:06:31,800
- 不要 苏莱曼 - 妈妈
- No, Sulayman. - Mama-jan.

881
01:06:31,800 --> 01:06:35,270
- 你赶不回来的 - 让她去吧
- You won't come back. - Let her go now.

882
01:06:35,270 --> 01:06:37,400
让帕瓦尔娜去吧
Let Parvana go.

883
01:06:44,610 --> 01:06:46,550
哦
Oh!

884
01:06:53,450 --> 01:06:55,560
帕瓦尔娜
Parvana.

885
01:07:31,590 --> 01:07:33,230
德利瓦
Deliwar!

886
01:07:34,660 --> 01:07:37,600
你差点把我吓死
You frightened me half to death.

887
01:07:37,600 --> 01:07:39,600
我一直在到处找你
I've been looking for you everywhere.

888
01:07:39,600 --> 01:07:42,530
找我干嘛？想跟我一起去柴家商店干活吗？
Why? You want to work at the chai shop with me this morning?

889
01:07:42,530 --> 01:07:46,440
- 不 我不行 - 嘿 你想给扎西弄些糖果吗？
- No, I can't. - Hey, you want some candy for Zaki?

890
01:07:46,440 --> 01:07:49,280
明天我们就要离开喀布尔
We are leaving Kabul tomorrow.

891
01:07:50,880 --> 01:07:52,740
你要离开我吗？
You are leaving me?

892
01:07:52,750 --> 01:07:55,880
家里都安排好了 我也无能为力
It's been arranged. There's nothing I can do.

893
01:07:55,880 --> 01:08:00,020
我姐姐就要去马札里沙里夫结婚了
My sister is getting married in Mazar-e-Sharif.

894
01:08:00,020 --> 01:08:01,620
我还要再去一次监狱
I'm going back to the prison.

895
01:08:01,620 --> 01:08:03,620
我找到了一个能帮我的人
I found someone who can help me,

896
01:08:03,620 --> 01:08:05,860
而且我需要更多的钱来贿赂看守
and I need to get more money to bribe the guard.

897
01:08:05,860 --> 01:08:07,760
今天是最后期限了
I'll need it today.

898
01:08:07,760 --> 01:08:10,930
你只会挨更多拳头的 这个想法很愚蠢
You'll just get another punch in the guts. It's a stupid idea.

899
01:08:10,930 --> 01:08:12,760
这次不会的
I won't let that happen this time.

900
01:08:12,770 --> 01:08:15,900
- 我说了这个想法很愚蠢 - 求你了帮帮我吧
- I said it's a stupid idea. - Please help me.

901
01:08:15,900 --> 01:08:17,770
你想让我怎么做？
What do you want me to do?

902
01:08:17,770 --> 01:08:21,040
像你的儿童故事里那样 用魔法变出一些钱来给你吗？
Magic some money into your hand like in your kids' stories?

903
01:08:21,040 --> 01:08:23,740
那是行不通的 帕瓦尔娜
It doesn't work like that, Parvana.

904
01:08:23,740 --> 01:08:25,710
我帮不了你
I can't help you.

905
01:08:25,710 --> 01:08:29,810
赶紧逃到马札里沙里夫 然后享受那美好的婚礼吧
Now run away to Mazar-e-Sharif and have a nice wedding party.

906
01:08:29,820 --> 01:08:33,920
也许他们也会给你配个丈夫 你的麻烦就都不存在了
Maybe they'll find a husband for you too and your troubles will be over.

907
01:08:33,920 --> 01:08:36,350
至少能挺到婚礼结束
Until after the wedding, at least.

908
01:08:36,360 --> 01:08:37,790
你这个傻瓜
You fool!

909
01:08:40,930 --> 01:08:42,600
德利瓦
Deliwar!

910
01:08:43,660 --> 01:08:45,300
什沃吉亚
Shauzia.

911
01:08:53,810 --> 01:08:55,940
什沃吉亚
Shauzia.

912
01:08:55,940 --> 01:08:57,870
和我们一起走吧
Come with us.

913
01:08:57,880 --> 01:09:00,410
我不能
I can't.

914
01:09:00,410 --> 01:09:03,550
我爸爸会一直追到马札然后杀了我的
My father would come all the way to Mazar to kill me.

915
01:09:05,420 --> 01:09:08,420
我不能就这样离开喀布尔 帕瓦尔娜
I can't leave Kabul, Parvana, not like this.

916
01:09:10,620 --> 01:09:13,360
- 这儿 拿着 - 我不能拿你的钱
- Here, take this. - I can't take your money.

917
01:09:13,360 --> 01:09:15,330
你就拿着吧
Please take it.

918
01:09:18,430 --> 01:09:20,830
去看你爸爸吧
Go and see your Baba.

919
01:09:20,830 --> 01:09:24,900
告诉他 他有一个好女儿
Tell him that his daughter is a good daughter.

920
01:09:24,900 --> 01:09:28,580
告诉他 德利瓦说的
Tell him that Deliwar said so.

921
01:09:34,850 --> 01:09:37,580
嘿 德利瓦
Hey, Deliwar.

922
01:09:37,580 --> 01:09:39,720
怎么了？
What?

923
01:09:39,720 --> 01:09:42,450
20年后的今天 就在你之前提过的
I'll meet you at that beach you were talking about,

924
01:09:42,460 --> 01:09:45,120
那片月亮牵引海水的沙滩上
where the moon pulls the water,

925
01:09:45,120 --> 01:09:47,020
我等待和你再次相遇
20 years from today.

926
01:09:47,030 --> 01:09:50,160
我想那时我会认不出你来的 奥狄什
I don't think I'll recognize you then, Aatish.

927
01:09:50,160 --> 01:09:54,370
好吧 那你可以优惠卖我些漂亮的蓝石头
Well, you can sell me some pretty blue stones for a great price.

928
01:09:56,400 --> 01:09:58,470
后会有期
Until next time then.

929
01:10:01,470 --> 01:10:03,740
后会有期
Until next time.

930
01:10:21,790 --> 01:10:24,030
真主保佑你 你是费特马吗？
Peace be upon you. Are you Fattema?

931
01:10:24,030 --> 01:10:25,230
是的 我是费特马
Yes, I am Fattema.

932
01:10:25,230 --> 01:10:28,500
我是你的二表哥 穆罕默德·阿卜杜尔派我从马柞过来
I am your second cousin. Mohammed Abdul sent me from Mazar.

933
01:10:28,500 --> 01:10:30,870
叫上你的家人一起 我们现在就得走了
Gather your family. We must leave immediately.

934
01:10:30,870 --> 01:10:34,640
不 你看 你不应该这么早就来的
No, you see, you weren't supposed to come so soon.

935
01:10:34,640 --> 01:10:37,180
我儿子不在 我们必须等他回来
My son is away. We must wait for him to return.

936
01:10:37,180 --> 01:10:38,940
仗马上就打过来了 你没听说吗？
There is a war coming. Have you not heard?

937
01:10:38,950 --> 01:10:41,050
我们必须赶在他们封路之前离开
We have to leave now before they block the roads.

938
01:10:41,050 --> 01:10:43,810
我们必须等到她回家 我得等我的女儿
We have to wait until she comes home. I have to wait for my daughter.

939
01:10:43,820 --> 01:10:46,120
儿子？女儿？到底是哪一个？
Son? Daughter? Which is it?

940
01:10:46,120 --> 01:10:47,980
收拾东西 我们现在就要出发
Gather your things. We are leaving now!

941
01:10:47,990 --> 01:10:50,890
帕尔瓦娜回来前我是不会走的 我们必须等她回来
I'm not leaving without Parvana. We have to wait.

942
01:10:50,890 --> 01:10:52,890
我带你走已经算你走运的了 老女人
Count yourself lucky I'm taking you, old woman.

943
01:10:52,890 --> 01:10:54,890
这个女孩和那个孩子可更有价值
The girl and the baby are of more worth.

944
01:10:54,890 --> 01:10:56,790
我这趟可不能白来
I didn't come all this way for nothing.

945
01:10:56,800 --> 01:10:59,230
要是现在不走 我们就无法离开这里了
If we do not go now, we won't get out of here at all.

946
01:10:59,230 --> 01:11:01,770
- 我的宝贝 把他给我 - 快跟我走
- My baby! Give him to me! - Let's go! Argh!

947
01:11:01,770 --> 01:11:03,670
扎西 扎西
Zaki! Zaki!

948
01:11:04,700 --> 01:11:07,240
把孩子给我 把他给我
Give me my baby. Give him to me!

949
01:11:07,240 --> 01:11:09,410
- 不要 把他给我 - 放开 放开
- No! Give him to me! - Let go! Let go!

950
01:11:24,560 --> 01:11:26,820
- 问安 孩子 - 问安
- Salaam, little one. - Salaam.

951
01:11:26,830 --> 01:11:30,130
你带着一根老人的拐杖打算去哪？
Where are you going to with an old man's stick?

952
01:11:30,130 --> 01:11:32,730
这是我爸爸的
It belongs to my Baba.

953
01:11:32,730 --> 01:11:35,700
我要带给他 到监狱里
I'm taking it to him, to the prison.

954
01:11:36,840 --> 01:11:38,470
我知道了
I see.

955
01:11:39,240 --> 01:11:41,470
我们顺路
We're going that way.

956
01:11:48,650 --> 01:11:50,280
把我的孩子给我
Give me my baby!

957
01:11:50,280 --> 01:11:53,820
- 快跟我走 如果你还想要这孩子 就跟我走 - 扎西
- Let's go! If you want to keep the baby, come with me! - Zaki!

958
01:11:53,820 --> 01:11:55,850
我女儿还在外面
My daughter is out there.

959
01:11:55,860 --> 01:11:58,260
那你为什么会愚蠢到让她一个人出去呢？
Then what kind of fool are you to have sent her out alone?

960
01:11:58,260 --> 01:12:01,160
上车 否则你今天可不止会失去一个孩子
Get in, or she won't be the only child you'll lose today!

961
01:12:01,160 --> 01:12:03,960
不要...把我的孩子给我
Don't... Give me my baby!

962
01:12:03,960 --> 01:12:05,860
叫这孩子别吵
Keep him quiet!

963
01:12:05,870 --> 01:12:07,830
我求你了
I am begging you.

964
01:12:07,830 --> 01:12:12,740
等等我的女儿
Wait for my daughter!

965
01:12:59,950 --> 01:13:03,190
来吧 苏拉娅 我们得生火了
Come, Soraya. We must start a fire.

966
01:13:04,990 --> 01:13:06,790
我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan.

967
01:13:06,790 --> 01:13:09,130
嘿 我找罗山
Hey! I am looking for Roshan.

968
01:13:09,130 --> 01:13:12,600
我找罗山 我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan. I am looking for Roshan.

969
01:13:12,600 --> 01:13:15,830
我找罗山 我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan. I am looking for Roshan.

970
01:13:15,830 --> 01:13:18,030
- 开门  - 离门远一点 你这笨蛋
- Open the door! - Get away from the door, you stupid kid!

971
01:13:18,040 --> 01:13:20,300
- 我找罗山  - 快滚
- I am looking for Roshan! - Get out of here!

972
01:13:20,310 --> 01:13:22,270
- 我找罗山- 你是傻子吗？
- I am looking for Roshan! - Are you stupid?

973
01:13:22,280 --> 01:13:23,870
- 我找罗山 - 闭嘴
- I am looking for Roshan. - Shut up!

974
01:13:23,880 --> 01:13:25,240
你在这干什么呢？
What are you doing here?

975
01:13:25,240 --> 01:13:28,180
没事了 他是我儿子
It's all right. He's my son.

976
01:13:28,180 --> 01:13:30,680
里边需要你
You're wanted inside.

977
01:13:32,380 --> 01:13:34,320
这个男孩欠一些管教
That boy needs some discipline.

978
01:13:34,320 --> 01:13:36,120
那是我的事
That's my business.

979
01:13:39,090 --> 01:13:42,890
我的真主啊 你来这干什么？
What in the name of the merciful are you doing here?

980
01:13:42,900 --> 01:13:46,360
今天是星期三 我来找你的表弟罗山
It's Wednesday. I've come to meet your cousin Roshan.

981
01:13:46,370 --> 01:13:49,630
那边已经开战了
There's a war started.

982
01:13:49,640 --> 01:13:51,770
罗山已参战去了
Roshan has gone to fight.

983
01:13:51,770 --> 01:13:56,040
我们被从城里带到监狱 来清除那些不愿为我们战斗的人
We've been brought from the city to clear the prison of anyone who won't fight for us.

984
01:13:57,280 --> 01:13:59,080
- 那个老师... - 他还活着吗？
- The teacher... - Is he alive?

985
01:13:59,080 --> 01:14:00,740
我不知道
I don't know.

986
01:14:00,750 --> 01:14:04,850
那个老师是我的父亲 我是帕尔瓦纳 他的女儿
The teacher is my father. I am Parvana, his daughter.

987
01:14:05,990 --> 01:14:08,660
救救他吧 求你了
Help him, please.

988
01:14:10,890 --> 01:14:14,020
太阳下山前我还没回来的话 你就赶紧跑
If I'm not back before the sun has gone down, you run.

989
01:14:14,030 --> 01:14:17,800
能跑多远就跑多远 千万不要停
Run as far away as you can from here and you keep on running.

990
01:14:17,800 --> 01:14:20,160
日落之后你绝不能待在这里 你明白吗？
You can't stay here after sunset. Do you understand?

991
01:14:20,170 --> 01:14:21,700
- 谢谢你 - 你明白了吗？
- Thank you. - Do you understand?

992
01:14:21,700 --> 01:14:23,830
- 是的 - 在那之前 你先藏起来
- Yes. - Hide yourself until then.

993
01:14:35,780 --> 01:14:39,880
从前有一个叫苏莱曼的男孩
Once there was a young boy called Sulayman.

994
01:14:39,890 --> 01:14:42,850
他知道他命中注定要为人民服务
He knew his heart was fated to serve his people,

995
01:14:42,860 --> 01:14:44,890
但他快没时间了
and he was running out of time.

996
01:14:53,800 --> 01:14:57,300
谢谢你 太谢谢你了
Thank you. Thank you so much.

997
01:14:57,300 --> 01:15:00,840
- 来吧 上车 - 我们得回去找我的女儿
- Come on! Get in the car. - We have to go back for my daughter.

998
01:15:00,840 --> 01:15:03,640
我说了 赶紧过来
I said come here. Now!

999
01:15:04,310 --> 01:15:06,240
我们不会跟你走的
We're not going with you.

1000
01:15:06,250 --> 01:15:08,050
妈妈？
Mama-jan?

1001
01:15:08,050 --> 01:15:11,150
你 过来 听不见我说话吗？
You, come now! Do you hear me?

1002
01:15:11,150 --> 01:15:14,920
让你过来你就过来
You come here like I told you to!

1003
01:15:16,120 --> 01:15:18,920
你现在就过来
You come now!

1004
01:15:20,060 --> 01:15:23,790
我们不会和你走的 你开车离开吧
We will not go with you. Just drive away from us.

1005
01:15:23,800 --> 01:15:27,130
上车 快上车
Get in the car. Get in the car now!

1006
01:15:27,130 --> 01:15:29,270
妈妈
Mama-jan!

1007
01:15:33,770 --> 01:15:36,940
苏莱曼 苏莱曼
Sulayman! Sulayman!

1008
01:15:38,480 --> 01:15:40,810
勇敢点 苏莱曼
Be brave, Sulayman.

1009
01:16:31,300 --> 01:16:33,060
快跑 苏拉娅
Run, Soraya.

1010
01:16:33,070 --> 01:16:35,270
- 现在带着扎西快跑  - 妈妈
- Take Zaki and run now! - Mama!

1011
01:16:35,270 --> 01:16:37,300
快走 一直跑
Go! Keep running!

1012
01:16:41,970 --> 01:16:46,010
你..让我们..走
You... let... us... go.

1013
01:16:56,590 --> 01:16:58,490
开门
Open the door.

1014
01:16:58,490 --> 01:16:59,960
你背着那个人干什么？
What are you doing with that?

1015
01:16:59,960 --> 01:17:03,760
他已经死了 我要把他和其他尸体放在一起 开门 让我过去
He's dead. I'm putting him with the others. Open the door. Let me through.

1016
01:17:18,580 --> 01:17:20,280
- 都快点走  - 站住
- Move, move, move, move, move! - Stop!

1017
01:17:20,280 --> 01:17:23,850
- 所有人 排成一行 - 站住
- Line up. All of you, all of you. - Stop!

1018
01:17:23,850 --> 01:17:25,420
我说了 站住
I said stop!

1019
01:17:25,420 --> 01:17:27,590
天快要黑了
It will be dark soon.

1020
01:17:27,590 --> 01:17:30,190
拉扎克
Razaq?

1021
01:17:30,190 --> 01:17:32,190
拉扎克？ 拉扎克？
Razaq? Razaq?

1022
01:17:43,570 --> 01:17:45,540
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

1023
01:17:45,540 --> 01:17:47,810
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

1024
01:17:48,340 --> 01:17:49,610
镜子可以反射光！
The mirror shines!

1025
01:17:49,610 --> 01:17:51,950
闪瞎那些怪物
Use it to blind the jaguars!

1026
01:18:04,260 --> 01:18:07,360
然后用网罩住他们
The net ensnares! Throw it over them!

1027
01:18:07,360 --> 01:18:09,830
哈
Hah!

1028
01:18:44,700 --> 01:18:47,160
拉扎克 拉扎克
Razaq. Razaq!

1029
01:18:47,170 --> 01:18:50,000
拉扎克 我来找我的父亲
Razaq! I have come for my father.

1030
01:18:50,000 --> 01:18:51,910
我来找我的父亲
I have come for my Baba!

1031
01:18:52,540 --> 01:18:55,040
把他放下来
Put him down!

1032
01:18:55,040 --> 01:18:57,140
我说了把他放下
I said put him down.

1033
01:19:02,510 --> 01:19:05,150
你了解现在的状况吗？
Do you see what is happening?

1034
01:19:05,150 --> 01:19:08,390
你把他带到哪里去？ 谁在外面？
Where are you taking him? Who's out there?

1035
01:19:08,390 --> 01:19:10,990
你就不能睁一只眼闭一只眼吗？
Look away, can't you?

1036
01:19:10,990 --> 01:19:13,160
现在这么乱 放过这个男人又能如何？
It is just one man. What does it matter?

1037
01:19:16,960 --> 01:19:19,560
走
Go.

1038
01:19:19,570 --> 01:19:21,360
走
Go!

1039
01:19:21,370 --> 01:19:23,300
走 除非你要杀了我
Go, unless you're going to kill me.

1040
01:19:27,010 --> 01:19:29,670
我会尖叫并诅咒你
I will scream and curse you

1041
01:19:29,670 --> 01:19:33,680
直到我用尽最后一口气
until the last breath leaves my body.

1042
01:19:33,680 --> 01:19:35,380
来吧
Go.

1043
01:19:38,620 --> 01:19:41,450
你疯了 疯了
You're crazy. Crazy.

1044
01:19:43,050 --> 01:19:45,290
你死在这都与我无关
You can die out here for all I care.

1045
01:19:45,720 --> 01:19:47,060
去死吧
Die.

1046
01:20:10,720 --> 01:20:12,490
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

1047
01:20:13,550 --> 01:20:15,160
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

1048
01:20:16,360 --> 01:20:17,620
苏莱曼
Sulayman.

1049
01:20:24,800 --> 01:20:27,230
我不是来杀你的
I have not come to kill you.

1050
01:20:38,040 --> 01:20:39,780
苏莱曼
Sulayman!

1051
01:20:39,780 --> 01:20:41,510
用你的故事让他平静下来
Soothe him with your story,

1052
01:20:41,510 --> 01:20:44,310
那个妈妈从没说起过的故事
the one that Mama-jan can't speak of.

1053
01:20:44,320 --> 01:20:45,750
告诉他
Tell him.

1054
01:20:45,750 --> 01:20:47,650
苏莱曼
Sulayman!

1055
01:20:47,650 --> 01:20:49,650
我叫苏莱曼
My name is Sulayman.

1056
01:20:49,660 --> 01:20:51,760
告诉他发生了什么
Tell him what happened.

1057
01:20:51,760 --> 01:20:54,430
告诉他你的故事
Tell him your story.

1058
01:20:54,430 --> 01:20:55,790
我叫苏莱曼
My name is Sulayman.

1059
01:20:55,790 --> 01:20:58,100
我的母亲是一个作家
My mother is a writer.

1060
01:20:58,100 --> 01:20:59,830
我父亲是一个老师
My father is a teacher.

1061
01:20:59,830 --> 01:21:03,370
我的妹妹们总在争吵
And my sisters always fight each other.

1062
01:21:03,370 --> 01:21:05,770
有天我在街上发现一个玩具
One day I found a toy on the street.

1063
01:21:05,770 --> 01:21:07,740
就把它捡了起来
I picked it up.

1064
01:21:07,740 --> 01:21:09,470
它爆炸了
It exploded.

1065
01:21:11,180 --> 01:21:13,810
我不记得后面发生了什么
I don't remember what happened after that

1066
01:21:13,810 --> 01:21:15,610
因为这就是结局
because it was the end.

1067
01:21:15,610 --> 01:21:18,650
起作用了 苏莱曼 继续讲 继续跟他讲
It's working, Sulayman! Tell him. Tell him!

