象王对男孩的态度发生了转变
The Elephant was transformed.

1087
01:22:10,470 --> 01:22:12,870
他从山峦中拿出那袋种子
He took the bag of seed from the center of the mountain

1088
01:22:12,870 --> 01:22:15,440
还给了苏莱曼
and gave it back to Sulayman.

1089
01:22:15,440 --> 01:22:18,440
苏莱曼回到他的家乡
Sulayman returned to his village.

1090
01:22:18,440 --> 01:22:21,680
村民们载歌载舞
There was much dancing and singing

1091
01:22:21,680 --> 01:22:24,250
开怀大吃
and laughing and eating.

1092
01:22:31,690 --> 01:22:33,360
拉扎克？
Razaq?

1093
01:22:39,600 --> 01:22:40,860
爸爸？
Baba?

1094
01:22:40,870 --> 01:22:43,500
爸爸  他还活着吗？
Baba! Is he alive?

1095
01:22:44,900 --> 01:22:48,400
这不是他的血 他还活着
It is not his blood. He lives.

1096
01:23:08,830 --> 01:23:11,600
离开这里 孩子 快走吧
Get out of here now, child. Go on.

1097
01:23:11,600 --> 01:23:14,270
全速离开此地
As fast as you can.

1098
01:24:17,960 --> 01:24:19,760
这是月亮
It's the moon.

1099
01:24:26,970 --> 01:24:28,610
苏拉娅
Soraya.

1100
01:24:29,540 --> 01:24:32,740
苏……拉娅
S... Sora... Soraya!

1101
01:24:32,750 --> 01:24:34,980
- 妈妈？ - 苏拉娅
- Mama? - Soraya!

1102
01:24:34,980 --> 01:24:37,350
苏……
So...

1103
01:24:41,950 --> 01:24:46,260
在我们家乡 人才是最无价的珍宝
We are a land whose people are its greatest treasure.

1104
01:24:50,630 --> 01:24:54,630
我们的家乡是在两个交战国的边境交汇处
We are at the edges of empires at war with each other.

1105
01:24:56,970 --> 01:24:58,610
帕尔……
Par...

1106
01:25:00,640 --> 01:25:02,570
帕尔瓦娜
Parvana.

1107
01:25:04,340 --> 01:25:08,680
我们的家园在兴都库什山脉的利爪下被分成数个部分
We are a fractured land in the claws of the Hindu Kush mountains,

1108
01:25:08,680 --> 01:25:12,250
有北部沙漠那炽烈之眼的灼热
scorched by the fiery eyes of the northern deserts.

1109
01:25:13,550 --> 01:25:17,720
亦包括那黑白交汇的冰峰之凛冽
Black rubble earth against ice peaks.

1110
01:25:19,330 --> 01:25:22,790
我们的家园叫阿里亚纳
We are Ariana,

1111
01:25:22,790 --> 01:25:25,730
是高尚之乡
the land of the noble.

1112
01:25:27,100 --> 01:25:30,730
话要说的更有道理 而不是提高音量
Raise your words, not your voice.

1113
01:25:30,740 --> 01:25:33,940
毕竟是雨水滋润花朵生长
It is rain that makes the flowers grow,

1114
01:25:33,940 --> 01:25:36,340
而不是雷鸣
not thunder.


